  configurationsettings
  Configuration
  


		  The configuration dialog can be invoked at any time via the "File" menu.
		  It is also opened automatically the first time JGlideMon is run.
  



		  Many settings are global and used for each Glider connection but some
		  are specific to a particular connection, the host, for example. Server
		  specific settings are indicated with an asterisk (*).
  

